author: IGN
description:
Monster Hunter Wilds is far, far from over after you’ve reached the credits, which really just act to signify the transition from Low Rank to High Rank. High Rank hunts are harder for one, and though the story continues, the structure of the gameplay loop changes substantially. 

In this guide to Monster Hunter Wilds’ High Rank and endgame we’ll cover what you should do between story quests and beyond, what you’ll get for doing side missions, and why and how you should be doing things like hunting Tempered monsters, crafting Artian Weapons, and farming Decorations– complete with tips you’ll need to know to make the most of everything.

Timecodes:

00:00 - Intro
00:39 - Hunter Rank and Assignments
01:29 - How to Change Time of Day/Weather
02:00 - Side Missions (Armorcharm and Powercharm)
02:35 - Resources Gatherer Unlocks
02:53 - Palico Sidequests and Weather Effects
03:13 - Field Surveys
03:49 - Investigations
04:41 - Optional Quests
04:54 - High Rank Loop
05:20 - Endgame After Assig
title: Monster Hunter Wilds: Your Guide to High Rank and ENDGAME

author: IGN
description:
Watch the latest The Alters trailer to see how the upcoming sci-fi personal survival game from 11 bit studios shares similar themes with the studio's 2014 game survival strategy game, This War of Mine. The Alters will be available on PC, PS5 (PlayStation 5), and Xbox Series X|S, also in Xbox Game Pass and PC Game Pass in 2025.

At their core, both games are about survival. In This War of Mine, days and nights pass as you do whatever it takes to outlast the war in a besieged city. In The Alters, survival is a race against time—a relentless battle against a scorching sun that will turn everything to dust if you fail to keep your mobile base moving.

#TheAlters #Gaming #Games
title: The Alters - Official This War of Mine Comparison Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Check out our first Blades of Fire preview! When I sat down to play developer MercurySteam’s latest project, Blades of Fire, I expected something of a return to the studio’s Castlevania: Lords of Shadow games, updated with the modern stylings of God of War. An hour later I thought I was playing a Soulslike, albeit one where all the stats were in my weapons rather than an RPG character sheet. By the end of the three-hour hands-on session, I realised both of those observations were simultaneously true and false: this is a game that is unmistakably built on well-worn ground, but the unique arrangement of both its borrowed components and new ideas results in a fresh and interesting approach to the action-adventure genre. Don't miss our impressions and a look at some Blades of Fire gameplay!

#Gaming #BladesOfFire #Games
title: Blades of Fire Is the Action Game for Sword Obsessives

author: IGN
description:
Check out this WWE 2K25 Bloodline Rules gameplay, featuring a match with WWE Champion Cody Rhodes defending against bad guy John Cena.

Bloodline Rules is a brand new WWE 2K25 match type and allows you to use the new Bloodline Run-In payback to call for back up three times during the match. To test this mode out we created the Wrestlemania 41 main event of Cody Rhodes vs John Cena and watched the madness unfold.

John Cena's entrance and entire was edited to suit the new heel Cena persona and their allies were adjusted so we'd get (somewhat) realistic run-ins. It was also a Bloodline Rules match on Legend difficulty.

00:00 - John Cena's Heel Entrance
01:29 - Cody Rhodes Entrance
03:15 - Bloodline Rules Match

#WWE #WWE2K25 #Wrestling

description:
Jon Bernthal is back as Frank Castle, a.k.a. The Punisher! And now he's officially part of the Marvel Cinematic Universe thanks to his appearance in Daredevil: Born Again, which has been confirmed in trailers and by the show's producers.
Mild spoilers follow for Daredevil: Born Again's first two episodes!
So with Born Again Episode 1 and Episode 2 out this week on Disney+, we spoke to showrunner/executive producer Dario Scardapane and executive producer Sana Amanat about Frank's return, which is teased in the second episode.
Scardapane previously served as a producer and writer on the Netflix Punisher series, and he notes that the scene when Matt finds himself up against the dirty cops who framed White Tiger (the late Kamar de los Reyes) is definitely setting up the Punisher's return -- specifically in the form of a Punisher tattoo on one of the cops’ arms.

title: Daredevil: Born Again Creator Explains the Punisher Story That's 'Begging to Be Told'

author: IGN
description:
In today's Daily Fix:
The popular communications service Discord could become a publicly traded company in the future. The service has proven a hit with gamers and content creators, who use it for voice chat and group messaging, and so far it's been relatively devoid of third-party ads. But gamers are now worried that Discord going IPO could bring with it a deluge of ads. In other news, beta testers in the Xbox Insider program are urged caution when trying out the latest Xbox update. Users are reporting their profiles being removed from their consoles after the update. And finally, Sony has dropped some new gear: a Last of Us-branded DualSense controller with icons commemorating Ellie and Abby's dual journey in the acclaimed game saga.

#IGN
title: Discord's Plans to Go Public Have Gamers Worried About Ads - IGN Daily Fix
